<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Heavenly Seed Ministries | Sowing Hope</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* CSS DESIGN SYSTEM */
        :root {
            --deep-green: #0a2e07; /* Your Logo Green */
            --accent-gold: #c5a021; /* Your Logo Gold */
            --soft-cream: #fdfbf7;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; background-color: var(--soft-cream); color: #333; overflow-x: hidden; }

        /* Navigation */
        nav { 
            background: var(--deep-green); 
            padding: 10px 8%; 
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent-gold);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .logo-area { display: flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo-area img { height: 55px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); margin-right: 12px; }
        .logo-area h1 { color: var(--accent-gold); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        .nav-links { list-style: none; display: flex; }
        .nav-links a { color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 25px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent-gold); }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero { 
            height: 90vh; 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80'); 
            background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; color: white;
        }
        .hero-box { background: var(--glass); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 50px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        .hero h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3.8rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        /* Services Grid */
        section { padding: 100px 10%; }
        .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .section-title h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: var(--deep-green); }
        .underline { width: 80px; height: 4px; background: var(--accent-gold); margin: 20px auto; border-radius: 2px; }

        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; }
        .card { 
            background: var(--white); padding: 45px 30px; border-radius: 25px; text-align: center; 
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: 0.5s; position: relative;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-15px); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(197, 160, 33, 0.15); }
        .card::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 5px; background: var(--accent-gold); border-radius: 25px 25px 0 0; opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s; }
        .card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        
        .icon { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)); }
        .card h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--deep-green); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.6rem; }

        /* Forms & Donations */
        .prayer-area { background: #f4f1ea; border-radius: 50px 50px 0 0; }
        .form-box { max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 50px; border-radius: 30px; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        input, select, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 15px; margin: 12px 0; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; background: #fafafa; font-family: inherit; }
        .btn { background: var(--deep-green); color: var(--accent-gold); padding: 18px; width: 100%; border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .btn:hover { background: var(--accent-gold); color: var(--deep-green); transform: scale(1.02); }

        .bank-info { 
            margin-top: 50px; background: var(--deep-green); color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 25px; 
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); text-align: center;
        }
        .bank-info h3 { color: var(--accent-gold); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        footer { background: #051a03; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 60px; border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-gold); }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="#" class="logo-area">
            <img src="logo.jpg" alt="Heavenly Seed Logo">
            <h1>HEAVENLY SEED</h1>
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#missions">Missions</a></li>
            <li><a href="#prayer">Prayer</a></li>
            <li><a href="#donate">Support Us</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-box">
            <p>SOWING THE SEEDS OF THE KINGDOM</p>
            <h2>"A farmer went out to sow..."</h2>
            <p style="border:none; font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.8;">Luke 8:5</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="missions">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Our Sacred Outreach</h2>
            <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">👵</span><h3>Old Age Home</h3><p>Comfort and dignity for our beloved elders.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">📚</span><h3>Education</h3><p>Hostels and schools for tribal children.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">🩺</span><h3>Hospital Aid</h3><p>Helping the poor clear medical bills.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">🍚</span><h3>Rice Bags</h3><p>Feeding families with monthly grocery support.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">🏔️</span><h3>Tribal Ministry</h3><p>Reaching the unreached in remote areas.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><span class="icon">🕊️</span><h3>Widow Help</h3><p>Financial and spiritual support for widows.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="prayer" class="prayer-area">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Prayer Request</h2>
            <div class="underline"></div>
            <p>Let us stand with you in faith.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="form-box">
            <form action="mailto:your-email@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
                <input type="text" name="Name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                <select name="Category">
                    <option>Healing</option>
                    <option>Finance</option>
                    <option>Family</option>
                </select>
                <textarea name="Message" rows="5" placeholder="How can we pray for you?"></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit Request</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="donate">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Support the Ministry</h2>
            <div class="underline"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bank-info">
            <h3>Bank Transfer Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Account Name:</strong> Heavenly Seed Ministries</p>
            <p><strong>Account Number:</strong> 0000 1111 2222 3333</p>
            <p><strong>Bank Name:</strong> State Bank | <strong>IFSC:</strong> SBIN0001234</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Heavenly Seed Ministries. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p style="color: var(--accent-gold); margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.8rem;">Dedicated to Sowing Love and Harvesting Hope.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
